{"tid":2511042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地傳禁運名牌波鞋到港 Buyandship：事出突然未知解封期 大陸海關否認","createTime":"2021-04-30T14:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T08:43:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6785df0e7972d0f933edffe03aa2b5ac8437024b","tid":2511042,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"網購轉運公司Buyandship網站顯示，在禁運品目錄中「知名品牌鞋履」一項，包括「Nike、Adidas、Fila等知名品牌的鞋子」，Buyandship聲稱因應中國海關新規定，暫時無法運往香港，《蘋果》以顧客身份向公司客服查詢，對方指是今周收到突發通知，暫時未知禁運期何時完結，但中國海關卻稱，「沒有說哪個品牌不讓郵寄」。<br />\n<br />\nBuyandship客服人員表示，今周突然收到通知，因應快接近中共黨慶一百周年，內地有新配套禁止不同類別貨物運送到港，而名牌鞋為其中之一。為配合相關政策，倉庫會拒收所有來自潮流網購App「得物」之貨物，及所有註明為名牌球鞋的貨物。而且不作額外通知。呼籲用家若仍有購買有關類別貨物並未派到倉庫，應盡快安排取消訂單，或轉寄其他地址。<br />\n<br />\n客服人員又指，今次是突發事件，收到通知後已即時通知會員，目前未清楚何時會解封。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210430/UGLNMIG2PNHB5LY7SBCKZ4XLZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210430%2FUGLNMIG2PNHB5LY7SBCKZ4XLZE%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ff992b74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210430%2FUGLNMIG2PNHB5LY7SBCKZ4XLZE%2F&h=74589a69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210430/UGLNMIG2PNHB5LY7SBCKZ4XLZE/</a>"},{"pid":"1f4523a557afc7fe7de437ca904e1e7fd97ecb3d","tid":2511042,"uid":385411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"被共<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e32b0b07f5d7e4cb6fb7d15e08e9726d081e298","tid":2511042,"uid":35418,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"中国肯認先係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a4901031a89b5fc8714367fa42d92a853729d6","tid":2511042,"uid":342990,"like":